)BODY EXPAND(@@)
%TUTORIAL @-@  Rockwell added LISTA     Primary Command  @-@ TUTORIAL
%OPTION ===>_ZCMD
%
+  The%LISTA+command allows you to use a full-screen version of the TSO
   LIST your ALLOCATED files.  You may then select using line commands
   the following functions: Browse, Edit, PDS command, LISTSP, hardcopy
   Free file and dataset Enqueue checking.

+Syntax:
%    LISTA
%    LISTA  ddname
%    LISTA  ddname1 ddname2
%    LISTA  FULL
+
+Operands:
+    ddname -  a name of a currently allocated file or ddname
+    FULL   -  show full list of all datasets allocated to each ddname
               Default list only shows first dataset allocated for each
+
+Note: If LISTA is invoked using TSO LISTA command operands, then
   the output of TSO LISTA command will be displayed in browse mode.
+
)PROC
  .RESP = END
)END
